### Candidate Management with Google Drive Integration

### NOTE: Replace YOUR_TOKEN and CANDIDATE_ID with actual values

### 1. Add Candidate (with Resume Upload)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/candidates
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="firstName"

John
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="lastName"

Doe
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="email"

john.doe@example.com
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="phone"

9876543210
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="skills"

["JavaScript","React","Node.js"]
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="experience"

3
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="jobRole"

Frontend Developer
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resume"; filename="resume.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-resume.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### 2. Get All Candidates
GET http://localhost:5000/api/candidates
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 3. Get Candidate by ID (includes resume info)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/CANDIDATE_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 4. Update Candidate (without changing resume)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/CANDIDATE_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "experience": 4
}

###

### 5. Update Candidate (with new resume)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/CANDIDATE_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="firstName"

John
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="lastName"

Smith
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="experience"

4
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resume"; filename="updated-resume.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./updated-resume.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### 6. Download/View Resume
GET http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/CANDIDATE_ID/resume
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 7. Update Candidate Status
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/CANDIDATE_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Shortlisted"
}

###

### 8. Delete Candidate (also deletes resume from Google Drive)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/CANDIDATE_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 9. Get Status Counts
GET http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/stats/status-counts
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 10. Get All Skills
GET http://localhost:5000/api/candidates/stats/skills
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### 11. Search Candidates with Filters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/candidates?search=john&status=Applied&jobRole=Developer&experienceLevel=Mid-Level&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###
